transcript:

Customer: Hello. A to Z production se baat ho rahi hai?
Executive: Hmm.
Executive: Good evening sir, main baat kar rahi hoon servicing team India Mart se.
Customer: Boliye na.
Executive: Sir basically main aap main aap se ye jaanna chah rahi hoon ki sir abhi aap by lead consume kyun nahi kar rahe ho?
Customer: Kya madam wohi wohi case repeat aap log ko bata rahe hain.
Customer: Consume kya karenge? Aligarh ki aa rahi hai inquiry. Aligarh mein business hai kya?
Executive: Aapko sir kaha ki chahiye mainly?
Customer: Woh chod dijiye abhi call cut karke.
Customer: Jab tak aap issue
